START PROGRAM

Create ArrayList days
Create ArrayList temp

Add "Monday" to days
Add "Tuesday" to days
Add "Wednesday" to days
Add "Thursday" to days
Add "Friday" to days
Add "Saturday" to days
Add "Sunday" to days

Create Scanner object

FOR index from 0 to size of days - 1
    Prompt user to enter average temperature for days[index]
    Read temperature value
    Add temperature to temp list
END FOR

Clear scanner input buffer

Prompt user to enter a day of the week or "week"
Read user input

IF user input equals "week"
    Set total to 0

    Display "Weekly Temperatures"

    FOR index from 0 to size of days - 1
        Display days[index] and temp[index]
        Add temp[index] to total
    END FOR

    Calculate weeklyAverage = total / number of temperatures
    Display weeklyAverage

ELSE
    Set found flag to false

    FOR index from 0 to size of days - 1
        IF days[index] equals user input
            Display days[index] and temp[index]
            Set found flag to true
            Exit loop
        END IF
    END FOR

    IF found is false
        Display "Invalid day entered"
    END IF
END IF

Close Scanner

END PROGRAM


